Changelog for phplist  2007-02-26 22:11

2007-02-26 20:51  mdethmers

	* updated processqueue to clear page cache before starting sending

2007-02-26 20:50  mdethmers

	* added function to clear all cached pages from the database

2007-02-26 16:13  mdethmers

	* update to message envelope, set it to the configured "person in
	  charge" if it's not set, so that bounces will go to this person,
	  instead of into oblivion (generally)

2007-02-26 15:37  mdethmers

	* added flushing of click track stats to preserve memory

2007-02-26 09:41  mdethmers

	* updated portuguese (brazilian) and dutch frontend translations

2007-02-25 23:41  mdethmers

	* added retrieving interval in timer, so that the time between
	  blocks can be tracked

2007-02-25 23:39  mdethmers

	* added sql_fetch_assoc to mysql.inc

2007-02-22 23:35  mdethmers

	* added calculation of message sizes and complete size of mailblast
	  to misc tab in send a message page

2007-02-22 23:34  mdethmers

	* update to store the estimated size of the email going out in the
	  database, so the bandwidth usage can be calculated.

2007-02-22 23:26  mdethmers

	* update loading of message data to properly load serialized data,
	  and add function to turn bytes into G/M/k bytes for display

2007-02-22 21:27  mdethmers

	* added link from list page to listbounces page

2007-02-22 21:26  mdethmers

	* added link from bounces page to listbounces page

2007-02-22 21:25  mdethmers

	* updated merging of duplicates to allow deletion of the duplicate
	  one after merging

2007-02-22 21:23  mdethmers

	* added option to also blacklist emails when mass unconfirming them

2007-02-22 21:23  mdethmers

	* added calculation of size of email to phpmailer

2007-02-22 21:22  mdethmers

	* added AjaxRequest library

2007-02-22 21:21  mdethmers

	* added favicon in backend

2007-02-22 21:20  mdethmers

	* added logging of import results to eventlog

2007-02-21 01:59  mdethmers

	* updated db structure to add a flag that a user really personally
	  confirmed their subscription, as opposed to being imported

2007-02-21 01:57  mdethmers

	* updated default stats interval to be weekly, not monthly

2007-02-21 01:56  mdethmers

	* added ignore to verbose sql query

2007-02-21 01:55  mdethmers

	* added page tor reset click track statistics

2007-02-21 01:55  mdethmers

	* added page to (manually) rebuild the DB indexes, if they don't
	  exist.

2007-02-20 15:30  mdethmers

	* added "entrypoint" to session when using link tracking

2007-02-20 15:28  mdethmers

	* added a "click track linkmap" that can be used to make tracked
	  links look more professional, added the option to always add open
	  tracking, added the List Headers to mails when using phpmailer
	  and some changes to use more optimised replacement when using
	  php5

2007-02-20 15:24  mdethmers

	* added -f option to processqueue commandline, which will force
	  processing (and kill existing processes)

2007-02-20 15:23  mdethmers

	* changed processbounces to only send an email report if users were
	  actually processed and changed the email report to link to the
	  user account

2007-02-19 21:59  mdethmers

	* added option to place the language file in a different location,
	  so it can be more specific per site

2007-02-19 21:57  mdethmers

	* added memory caching of linktrack statistics that are flushed
	  regularly to reduce the number of DB queries when sending

2007-02-19 21:54  mdethmers

	* moved ending the header to a different place to handle change on
	  content types better, when used by plugins

2007-02-19 21:51  mdethmers

	* added logging of queries when in debug mode to see which ones
	  make most sense to optimize

2007-02-19 21:50  mdethmers

	* updated sessionlib to not use the DB sessions on link and open
	  tracking

2007-02-19 21:47  mdethmers

	* added option UPLOADIMAGES_DIR that can be used to point to a
	  directory in the webserver root for uploading images from the
	  FCKeditor

2007-02-19 21:46  mdethmers

	* updated phplist webbler plugin class to send confirmation
	  messages using the configured from field values

2007-02-01 17:15  mdethmers

	* update to only check on postcode if it's actually being used

2007-01-22 18:13  mdethmers

	* updated keymanager to switch itself off, if the settings are
	  incorrect

2007-01-22 18:12  mdethmers

	* updated userhistory to use the one in commonlib instead

2007-01-22 18:11  mdethmers

	* added option of exporting user changes to profile

2007-01-22 13:05  mdethmers

	* moved userhistory to commonlib

2007-01-19 13:50  mdethmers

	* added option to attributes with multiple values to add an
	  authoritative list by using a webbler keyword library

2007-01-02 16:32  mdethmers

	* merged changes from 2.10.x branch into main branch

