	* update of structure to revised structure

2006-12-11 17:04  mdethmers

	* updated upgrade

2006-12-11 17:03  mdethmers

	* revised way that clicktracking works, because the old method
	  creates too large database tables when used with many users,
	  emails and/or links

2006-12-11 17:01  mdethmers

	* added a column to the domain stats page, listing number of
	  unconfirmed users per domain

2006-12-11 17:00  mdethmers

	* added options to plugins to provide a list of "formats" that the
	  plugin can send messages in, to be used in the send message page
	  for an admin to choose the send format

2006-12-11 16:59  mdethmers

	* added new table definitions for revised click tracking

2006-12-11 16:58  mdethmers

	* updated phplist mailer class to allow plugins to manipulate
	  outgoing message by wrapping it in a seperate mime layer

2006-11-21 23:10  mdethmers

	* updated shader to work in IE7, which can't seem to handle images
	  with IDs

